Shared Memories Anomaly Season - Details
#SharedMemories
From July to September, Agents can take part in the Shared Memories Anomaly Season, competing across multiple Events to earn the most Season Points for their Faction. In addition, by taking part in some of these Events, Agents will be able to earn one or more of the Shared Memories Agent Profile medals. Early intelligence suggests that the Faction that wins the Shared Memories Season will affect childhood memories belonging to this universe‚Äôs Akira Tsukasa.

